OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and early part of the night
OL,7,Fwith some showers, and perhaps some
OL,8,Flonger spells of rain or sleet, with
OL,9,Fhill snow. Turning clearer with more
OL,10,Fisolated showers before morning.
OL,11,FStrengthening northwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA mixture of sunshine and
OL,14,Fblustery showers, heavy and wintry at
OL,15,Ftimes. Feeling unseasonably cold with
OL,16,Fa fresh north or northwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
